column5: Are there any launches near big bay pt?  I know there is one in Gilford but I was wondering if there were any closer to bbp either on the cooks bay side or the kbay side.
The Gov't dock has a spot where you could launch!   Turn left at the variety store & it will take you right to it!   Right in BBP, in the Kemp side!
Yeah I knw where you are talking about but I have a 2wd truck.  I don't know if there is anywhere to park a trailer either.

Beside Lake Simcoe Marina,south of the 5th line there is a free launch,but you have to park 2 blocks away (for free),just launch between the Marina ....and goverment dock.....TC and tight lines......Chuck.....
Yeah I know that one.  A bit far down and the ramp is not too good at all.  I will go there if all else fails.  Thanks
